\begin_layout Standard
A major subject to be discussed and agreed was to consolidate the ideas
 regarding the initiative aims and expectations.
 It was critical to better define the problem the initiative is attempting
 to contribute to and try to concretize the range of solutions available
 and which the initiative should pursue.
 In that sense the meeting was succefull and all these objectives were achieved.
 The discussions taken place gave raise to the definition of 
