 was the assessment model(s) to be explored, for which a set of characteristics
 were defined leaving open the exact framework to be used.
 A step further was taken by designing the type of Management Strategies
 Evaluation the initiative will promote/develop as a standard advise methodology
 for these kind of stocks.
 In a more operational setting the group defined a simulation experiment
 to be carried out and a set of subjects to be tested.
